id: pm-hvt3
title: "Nightly macOS+Windows red post-PR#568: staging-base selection compares realpath'd source against non-canonical temp dir — staging lands inside source, fs.cp EINVAL self-copy"
description: "Fix the residual cross-platform extension-copy staging regression left after PR #568: canonicalize the configured temporary directory before containment checks so macOS and Windows nightly installs cannot stage inside their own source."
