notes[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-19T11:31:35.066Z",maintainer-agent,"Fix implemented (branch mutation-integrity-and-sdk-batch-wave): copyExtensionDirectoryWithoutSelfNesting now canonicalizes temporaryDirectory via fs.realpath(path.resolve(...)) with resolveCanonicalExtensionInstallDestination as root-to-leaf fallback for missing temp dirs — same canonicalization family as source/destination, closing the third pm-0fhw-class asymmetry site. Two Linux-reproducible regression specs added to extension-copy-safety.spec.ts using symlink-aliased temp paths (junction on win32): both fail pre-fix with the exact nightly EINVAL signature, pass post-fix. No spec-side masking; PR CI now protects the macOS/Windows nightly failure mode without a platform matrix."
